title: Unverpackt
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Take-out, European, German, Non-veg
description: Vegetarian and organic food store with a coffee & smoothie bar and lunch service on Monday, Wednesday, and Friday. Sells a variety of dry goods like rice, nuts, beans, cereals, flours, coffee, tea, vegetable oils, vinegar, spices. Also sells local and seasonal fruit, vegetables.
